name: 2014 Iceland Calendar
description: This is a 12-page calendar featuring photographs from Iceland by Julia & Yuriy Manchik on each page. The back of each calendar page has a postcard back. Once the month passes, cut off the bottom of each page and send a postcard to a friend. Size: 6 x 8.75'' Printed on heavy matte card stock 1 bulldog clip included 15% of this sale will go to benefit His Kids Too.
